WEBVTT

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.736
Mening chin istagim o’zimni o’rganish

00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:32.976
va o’zgartirish edi.

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:35.616
Shu tariqa men 100 kunlik rad etilishni

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:37.536
o’yin maydoniga, tadqiqot

00:09:37.560 --> 00:09:39.696
loyihasiga aylantirdim.
Nima o'rgana olishim

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:41.800
mumkinligini ko’rmoqchi edim.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.016
Natijada ko’p narsalar o'rgandim.

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:45.616
Ko’plab sirlardan
boxabar bo'ldim.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:48.536
Misol uchun, shunga amin
bo’ldimki, agar men chekinmasam,

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:49.816
rad javobini olsm,
"yo'q"ni

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:51.896
“ha” ga aylantira
olishim mumkin.

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:53.536
Sehrli so’z esa, “nega?”

00:09:53.560 --> 00:09:57.656
Bir kuni qo’limda gul bilan bir notanish
kishining uyiga bordim, eshikni

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:59.096
taqillatib, shunday dedim:

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:01.376
shu gulni sizning tomorqangizda
eksam bo’ladimi?